1. INTRODUCTION  
1.1 PURPOSE 
This document describes the service delivery process for delivery manager or delegated person who 
implemented service. 
1.2 SCOPE 
The process is used in service delivery realized at 
 
However, in a certain service, the service manager or the delivery manager can decide whether to apply 
this entire process or just a modified version of it to the service, or leave it out.
